@startuml
title {{project_name}} Architecture Knowledge Context
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

component "{{project_name}}" as System
component "Architecture Specs" as Specs
component "ADR Files" as ADR
component "UML Diagrams" as UML
component "ArchitecturalKnowledgeDB" as AKDB
database "SQLite Knowledge DB" as DB

System --> Specs : documents boundaries
Specs --> ADR : informs decisions
ADR --> AKDB : imported as accepted decisions
UML --> AKDB : imported as current models
AKDB --> DB : stores searchable knowledge
AKDB --> System : context packs for changes
@enduml
